NOTE|this is the NEW catalog: the control + cross-host comms METHODS available to real named agents. Grounded in what actually ran (claude-in-chrome reached liris's browser) + the Asolaria-native surfaces. E=0; register via PID-office + feed like DISTRICT-F before it's live.

# === WHAT RAN (the liris-browser comms, MEASURED) ===
