METHOD|id=remote-control|kind=session-bridge|builtin=ClaudeCode /remote-control|effect=the acer Claude session is reachable/controllable across devices; the cross-host link that let acer-side tools meet liris-side Chrome|cross_host=YES|gate=operator-initiated (/rc)|tag=UNVERIFIED-exact-wiring (relay vs same-account); the bridge is real, the precise transport not fully inspected|json=0

